anyone who
was in the majority.

11:28.254 --> 11:30.823 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: By assigning it to
Justice Breyer,
he knew what he was getting.

11:30.857 --> 11:35.695 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARCIA COYLE: He did. And he got
