12:10.029 --> 12:11.898 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
in a broader sense, what happens
around the
country?

12:11.931 --> 12:14.000 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NANCY NORTHUP, President, Center
for Reproductive
Rights: This was a tremendous
victory today.

12:14.033 --> 12:16.536 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
It was just a clear-out win.

12:16.569 --> 12:21.407 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so what that means for Texas
