decision about
terminating a pregnancy.

19:02.308 --> 19:06.112 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so, as we see the fight is
going to go
ahead, we are going to see the
momentum be

19:06.145 --> 19:11.650 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
on the side. And the Supreme
Court's overwhelming
rejection of underhanded tactics
that they

19:11.684 --> 19:13.986 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
did today is a really good sign
for the future.

19:14.020 --> 19:17.456 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Nancy Northup,
president of the
Center for Reproductive Rights,
and Steven

19:17.490 --> 19:21.227 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Aden, senior counsel for
Alliance Defending
Freedom, thank you both very
much.

19:21.260 --> 19:24.897 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
NANCY NORTHUP: Thank you.

19:24.930 --> 19:29.502 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
STEVEN ADEN: Thank you, Gwen.

